Rating: 4
This is definitely one of the most fattening dishes I've made, but it was DELICIOUS!!! The only change I made was to use 1/2 cup whole wheat flour with 1 cup all purpose flour, which I highly recommend. The rustic flour goes well with the earthy mushrooms. I think I'll serve this as an appetizer next time I have a dinner party, but I will use individual tart pans and serve each tart on a bed of mixed greens. Divine.

